1645
01:11:56,620 --> 01:11:58,100
 Ili muško i žensko.

1646
01:11:58,100 --> 01:11:59,040
 Čak i to.

1647
01:11:59,040 --> 01:11:59,620
 Čak i to.

1648
01:11:59,620 --> 01:11:59,920
 Čak i to.

